# Persistence

- Apply the `shadowing-development` SOP and read ADR-0006/0007.
- Domain protocols define behavior; GRDB types stay inside Persistence.
- Migrations are forward-only, idempotent, and tested from previous schemas.
- Store recording audio as files and only stable relative paths in SQLite.
- Keep security-scoped bookmark API usage in Swift.
- Make file and metadata failure recovery explicit and testable.
